---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Venue" description="CloudConf 2026 venue information and directions">
  <style>
    .venue-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0e27 0%, #1a237e 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 3rem 0;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .venue-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .venue-hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #e0e0e0;
    }

    .venue-container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .venue-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .venue-info h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #0a0e27;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .venue-details {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .venue-details h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #0a0e27;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .venue-details p {
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .venue-details a {
      color: #0066cc;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .venue-details a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .venue-map {
      background: #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      height: 400px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .amenities {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .amenities h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #0a0e27;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .amenities-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .amenity-item {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border-left: 4px solid #64b5f6;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .amenity-item h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #0a0e27;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .amenity-item p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .transportation {
      background: #e3f2fd;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
    }

    .transportation h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #0a0e27;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .transportation h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #0066cc;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .transportation p {
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .venue-hero h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .venue-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .venue-map {
        height: 300px;
      }

      .venue-info h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <section class="venue-hero">
    <div class="venue-container">
      <h1>Venue Information</h1>
      <p>CloudConf 2026 | May 15, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="venue-container">
    <div class="venue-grid">
      <div class="venue-info">
        <h2>The Venue</h2>
        <div class="venue-details">
          <h3>📍 Location</h3>
          <p><strong>Moscone Center</strong></p>
          <p>747 Howard Street</p>
          <p>San Francisco, CA 94103</p>
          <p><a href="https://www.moscone.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visit Moscone Center Website</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="venue-details">
          <h3>🕐 Hours</h3>
          <p><strong>Registration:</strong> 8:00 AM</p>
          <p><strong>Event Start:</strong> 9:00 AM</p>
          <p><strong>Event End:</strong> 5:30 PM</p>
        </div>

        <div class="venue-details">
          <h3>🎟️ Parking</h3>
          <p>Parking is available at the Moscone Center garage. Discounted rates available for event attendees with validation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="venue-map">
        <div>
          <p>📍 Interactive map coming soon</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1rem; color: #999;">Moscone Center, San Francisco</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="amenities">
      <h2>Venue Amenities</h2>
      <div class="amenities-grid">
        <div class="amenity-item">
          <h3>☕ Catering</h3>
          <p>Breakfast, lunch, and refreshments provided throughout the day</p>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-item">
          <h3>📶 WiFi</h3>
          <p>High-speed WiFi available throughout the venue</p>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-item">
          <h3>♿ Accessibility</h3>
          <p>Fully accessible venue with elevators and accessible restrooms</p>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-item">
          <h3>🅿️ Parking</h3>
          <p>On-site parking available with discounted rates</p>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-item">
          <h3>🎤 AV Equipment</h3>
          <p>State-of-the-art audio and video equipment</p>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-item">
          <h3>🛎️ Support</h3>
          <p>On-site staff available to assist attendees</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="transportation">
      <h2>Getting There</h2>
      <h3>🚗 By Car</h3>
      <p>The Moscone Center is located in downtown San Francisco with easy freeway access. Parking is available on-site with discounted rates for attendees.</p>

      <h3>🚌 Public Transportation</h3>
      <p><strong>BART (Bay Area Rapid Transit):</strong> Take BART to the Civic Center or Powell Street stations, both within walking distance.</p>
      <p><strong>Muni:</strong> Multiple bus lines serve the area. Check <a href="https://www.sfmta.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SFMTA.com</a> for routes and schedules.</p>
      <p><strong>Cable Cars:</strong> Historic cable cars run nearby for a scenic option.</p>

      <h3>✈️ By Air</h3>
      <p><strong>San Francisco International Airport (SFO):</strong> 13 miles south. Take BART directly to downtown San Francisco.</p>
      <p><strong>Oakland International Airport (OAK):</strong> 40 miles east. Take BART or rental car.</p>
      <p><strong>San Jose International Airport (SJC):</strong> 50 miles south. Rental car or shuttle recommended.</p>

      <h3>🏨 Hotels</h3>
      <p>Many hotels are within walking distance of Moscone Center. We recommend booking early as San Francisco hotels fill up quickly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
